					<h1>CSS3 Flexible Box Layout: Everything I Wish I Knew When I Started</h1>

					<div data-component="EditButton" data-collection="articles" data-path="articles/2011-09-19-css3-flexible-box-layout-explained.md"></div>
				</header>

